 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# Differential Chromatin Interaction\n",
    "\n",
    "Do the DCI(differential chromatin interaction) analysis between two Hi-C matrics.\n",
    "The Selfish method used here is described in the paper:\n",
    "\n",
    "> Abbas Roayaei Ardakany, Ferhat Ay, Stefano Lonardi, Selfish: discovery of differential chromatin interactions via a self-similarity measure, Bioinformatics, Volume 35, Issue 14, July 2019, Pages i145–i153, https://doi.org/10.1093/bioinformatics/btz362\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "![](https://github.com/ay-lab/selfish/raw/master/demo.png)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import coolbox\n",
    "from coolbox.api import *"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "metadata": {
    "scrolled": true
   },
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "'0.3.0'"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 2,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "coolbox.__version__"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "data_dir = \"../../../tests/test_data/\"\n",
    "cl1 = f\"{data_dir}/cool_chr1_89000000_90400000_for_cmp_1.mcool\"\n",
    "cl2 = f\"{data_dir}/cool_chr1_89000000_90400000_for_cmp_2.mcool\"\n",
    "\n",
    "region = \"chr1:89237500-90307500\""
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "The `Selfish` track input two hic track(`Cool` or `DotHiC`), it perform the `selfish` algorithm on the local fetched matrics.\n",
    "Output the q-value(p-value after `fdr_bh` correction) of differential interaction analysis:"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 8,
   "metadata": {
    "scrolled": false,
    "tags": [
     "nbsphinx-thumbnail"
    ]
   },
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 1133.86x794.551 with 18 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 8,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "frame = XAxis() + \\\n",
    "    Cool(cl1) + MinValue(5e-4) + MaxValue(1e-1) + \\\n",
    "    Cool(cl2) + MinValue(5e-4) + MaxValue(1e-1) + \\\n",
    "    Selfish(cl1, cl2) + \\\n",
    "    XAxis()\n",
    "frame *= Feature(depth_ratio=0.35)\n",
    "frame.plot(region)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### CLI code"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 5,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "%%bash\n",
    "\n",
    "data_dir=\"/home/nanguage/Dropbox/workspace/THP_paper/data/cool\"\n",
    "cl1=\"${data_dir}/THPP.cool\"\n",
    "cl2=\"${data_dir}/Ra.cool\"\n",
    "\n",
    "coolbox add XAxis - \\\n",
    "start_with Feature --depth_ratio=\"0.35\" - \\\n",
    "    add Cool $cl1 - \\\n",
    "    add Cool $cl2 - \\\n",
    "    add Selfish $cl1 $cl2 - \\\n",
    "end_with - \\\n",
    "add XAxis - \\\n",
    "goto \"chr1:89237500-90307500\" - \\\n",
    "plot /tmp/test_coolbox_selfish.png"
   ]
  }
 ],
